#: functions.php:814
msgid "【COLORFUL SECTIONSとは？】"
msgstr "【What's COLORFUL SECTIONS?】"

#: functions.php:816
msgid ""
"<p>COLORFUL SECTIONSは、<br>\n"
"              複数のブロックであらかじめデザインされている<br>\n"
"              「セクション」単位のデザインテンプレートをご用意しています。"
"<br>\n"
"              <br>\n"
"              はじめてLPを作成される方や、素早くLPを作りたい方にオススメで"
"す。<br>\n"
"              <br>\n"
"              ＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿</p>\n"
"\n"
"              <h2>オススメの作り方</h2>\n"
"              <p>１:<br>\n"
"              「<a href=\"#blocks7\">LPの上部</a>」→「<a href=\"#blocks8\">LP"
"の中部</a>」→「<a href=\"#blocks9\">LPの下部</a>」の順番で、<br>\n"
"              お好きなセクションを設置していくと、効果的なLP構成に基づいた"
"<br>\n"
"              LPページが出来上がります。</p>\n"
"\n"
"              <p>２：<br>\n"
"              あとは、それぞれのセクションの文字や画像を置き換えるなど<br>\n"
"              ご自身のLPをつくっていきましょう！<br>\n"
"              ＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿<br>\n"
"              →<a href=\"https://lpcolorful.com/member/?page_id=70\" "
"target=\"_blank\">該当するマニュアルはこちら</a>(要ログイン)</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>COLORFUL SECTIONS has <br>\n"
"              The design templates which are pre-designed in multiple blocks "
"<br>\n"
"              available in \"sections\". <br>\n"
" <br>\n"
"              This is recommended for first-time LP designers and those who "
"want to create an LP quickly. <br>\n"
" <br>\n"
"              ＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿</p>\n"
"\n"
"              <h2> Recommended method of creation</h2>\n"
"              <p> 1: <br>\n"
"              Create the sections in this order: \" <a href=\"#blocks7\">Top "
"of LP,\"</a> \" <a href=\"#blocks8\">Middle of LP</a>,\" and then \" <a "
"href=\"#blocks9\">Bottom of LP</a>.\" <br>\n"
"              If you set up the sections of your choice, you can create an "
"LP page based on an effective LP structure. <br>\n"
" </p>LP page will be created.</p>\n"
"\n"
"              <p> 2: <br>\n"
"              Then, replace the text and images in each section, etc. <br>\n"
"              Create your own LP! <br>\n"
"              ＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿ <br>\n"
"              → <a href=\"https://lpcolorful.com/member/?page_id=70\" "
"target=\"_blank\">Click here for the relevant manual (</a> login required)</"
"p>"

